Add sqlite library in the lib/ folder, version used at the moment "sqlite-jdbc-3.7.15-M1".
You can find the source code in the src/ folder.
In the bin/ folder you can find the person.db file that is a little database (made with sqlite) that contains three records. 

Compilation command:
  javac -cp "../lib/*" *.java -d "../bin/"

Run with:
  java -classpath "../lib/*:." Main
